<%# Intent for this page:

This is the order fulfillment page for the merchant %>

Total Revenue
Total Revenue by status
Total number of orders by status

Filter orders displayed by status (merchant orders html)

Link to each individual order
A list of orders including at least one of my products:
    Each order item sold by me with a quantity and line-item subtotal
    A link to the item description page
    DateTime the order was placed
    Link to transition the order item to marked as shipped
    The current status of the order ("pending", "paid", "complete", "cancelled")

<table class="fulfillment_revenue_table">
    <thead>
    <tr>
        <th>Total Revenue</th>
        <th>Total Revenue by Status</th>
        <th>Total Number of Orders by Status</th>
    </tr>
    </thead>
  
  <tbody>
    <tr>
        <td><%= Order.total_revenue %></td>
        <td><%= Order.total_revenue_by_status(status)%></td>
        <td><%= Order.total_number_of_orders_by_status(status)%></td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<section class="list_of_orders">
<input list="statuses">

<datalist id="statuses">
  <option value="Pending">
  <option value="Paid">
  <option value="Completed">
  <option value="Cancelled">
</datalist>
<p>Sort orders by: <%%> </p>

<p class="orders-button"> <%= link_to "List of All Orders", merchant_orders_list_path, method: :get %> </p>